  1017	| `python_plugins:` without `--allow-python-plugins` | `load_python_plugins()` | `Plugin '<python_plugins>': Python plugins require --allow-python-plugins.` |
  1018	| Plugin `.py` file not found | `_load_python_class()` | `Plugin 'openclaw-v2': module 'openclaw_runner.py' not found. Searched (in order): [...]` |
  1019	| Class not found in module | `_load_python_class()` | `Plugin 'openclaw-v2': class 'OpenClawV2Plugin' not found in /path/to/file.py` |
  1020	| Class doesn't subclass `UnisonPlugin` | `_load_python_class()` | `Plugin 'openclaw-v2': class 'OpenClawV2Plugin' does not subclass UnisonPlugin` |
  1021	| Module import raises exception | `_load_python_class()` | `Plugin 'openclaw-v2': error executing /path/to/file.py: NameError: ...` |
  1022	| `validate_installation()` fails | `load_python_plugins()` | `Plugin 'openclaw-v2': installation check failed: binary not found on PATH` |
  1023	| Plugin crashes mid-run (timeout) | `UnisonPlugin.run()` | `AgentResult(success=False, error="Timeout after 600s")` — same as built-in failures |
  1024	| Plugin crashes mid-run (non-zero exit) | `UnisonPlugin.run()` | `AgentResult(success=False, error="Command exited with code 1")` |
  1025	| Runtime name not in built-ins or plugins | `_select_runner()` | `No runner for runtime: 'unknown-runtime'` (halts pipeline) |
  1026	
  1027	### 7.1 CLI Validation Output (`unison validate`)
