  1206	## 12. Summary
  1207	
  1208	The plugin system adds one YAML section (`cli_plugins:`), one optional YAML
  1209	section (`python_plugins:`), one new ABC (`UnisonPlugin`), and a registry
  1210	that bridges them. The primary path — declarative CLI plugins — requires no
  1211	Python code from the user and no trust escalation. The power-user path —
  1212	Python plugins — is gated behind an explicit CLI flag. Existing pipelines
  1213	work exactly as before. Users add custom runtimes with a 6-line YAML stanza
  1214	and zero source edits. All errors surface pre-flight with specific,
  1215	actionable messages.

