   151	    that the user must explicitly accept.
   152	
   153	    Subclasses MUST override:
   154	      - ``binary``: the CLI executable name (str)
   155	      - ``cli_flags``: default CLI flags (list[str])
   156	      - ``validate_installation``: check that the binary is callable
   157	
   158	    Subclasses MAY override:
   159	      - ``startup_grace``: extra seconds added to timeout (default 0)
   160	      - ``run``: for non-subprocess backends (HTTP, gRPC, etc.)
   161	      - ``_build_command``: for custom argument ordering
   162	      - ``_env``: extra environment variables injected at runtime
